program: (PARI) listA237424(lim)=my(v=List(),a,t); while(1, for(b=0,a, t=(10^a+10^b+1)/3; if(t>lim, return(Set(v))); listput(v, t)); a++)
do(lim)=my(v=List(),u=listA237424(lim),t); for(i=1,#u, for(j=1,i, t=u[i]*u[j]; if(t>lim,break); listput(v,t))); apply(n->n%10, Set(v)) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, May 13 2015
